data.description: Beautifully updated duplex off Monroe Ave. This property boasts two huge apartments perfect for your portfolio or for owner occupants! Both units have 3 bedrooms with large living rooms, some newer flooring and updates.  One unit has an additional half bath as well.  The upstairs unit has its own private open porch. Vinyl siding for easy exterior maintenance with tons of private off street parking makes this super convenient. All kitchen appliances are included and both units have laundry hookups!
